Package Service

Interface IService<T extends User,U extends BaseRepository>

Type Parameters:
T - the type of user managed by the service (e.g., Doctor, Patient).
U - the type of repository used by the service (e.g., DoctorRepository, PatientRepository).
All Known Implementing Classes:
AdministratorService, DoctorService, PatientService, PharmacistService, UserService
public interface IService<T extends User,U extends BaseRepository>
Generic interface for user-specific service classes. Provides common operations for managing users and accessing their repositories.
